'''Amal Bedjaoui''' (wavutse ku ya 27 Nyakanga 1963) ni umuyobozi wa filime yo muri [[Alijeriya]], producer, n'umwanditsi.

Yavukiye muri Algiers, yize ibijyanye no gukina filime muri kaminuza ya New York . Yarangije muri Institut des hautes études cinématographiques hanyuma abona Master of Advanced Studies in Sinema muri kaminuza ya Paris 1 Pantheon-Sorbonne mu 1987.  Amaze imyaka itari mike akora nk'umuyobozi wungirije akaba n'umuyobozi ushinzwe gutunganya amafilime y kandi nk'umuyobozi wungirije ushinzwe ibikino. Filime ye ya mbere ngufi, ''Une vue imprenable'', yasohotse mu 1993. Filime ye ya kabiri ngufi, ''Shoot me Angel'', yasohotse mu 1995 ahabwa igihembo cya Panorama mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Berlin . 

Mu 2002, yashinze isosiyete ikora filimi ya ML Productions. Umwaka ukurikira, yayoboye kandi akora firime yiminota 58 ''Un Fils'' .  ''Un fils'' ivuga amateka ya Selim, indaya y'umusore n'umubano we na madamu mukuru.  Igice kinini cya firime gihinduranya hagati y'umunsi usanzwe kumanywa, nka Selim guhura na se, hamwe nijoro aho ubushakashatsi bwerekeranye nigitsina. Yavuzwe nk "icyitegererezo cy’ubwenegihugu bushingiye ku gitsina." 

Bedjaoui ni umukobwa wumudiplomate akaba n'umunyapolitiki Mohammed Bedjaoui . 
